<%- include("partials/header") %>

<main class="container">

<section class="article-hero">
<h1>Best Cheese for Mac and Cheese</h1>

<p>
Choosing the right cheese can make the difference between good mac and cheese
and unforgettable mac and cheese. The best cheeses melt smoothly, add rich
flavor, and create the perfect creamy sauce.
</p>
</section>

<section class="cheese-grid">

<div class="cheese-card">
<h2>Cheddar</h2>
<p>The classic mac and cheese cheese. Sharp cheddar adds bold flavor while melting smoothly.</p>
</div>

<div class="cheese-card">
<h2>Gruyère</h2>
<p>Nutty and rich. Often used in gourmet mac and cheese recipes.</p>
</div>

<div class="cheese-card">
<h2>Gouda</h2>
<p>Slightly sweet and incredibly creamy when melted.</p>
</div>

<div class="cheese-card">
<h2>Mozzarella</h2>
<p>Great for that stretchy cheese pull, though milder in flavor.</p>
</div>

<div class="cheese-card">
<h2>Monterey Jack</h2>
<p>Very smooth melting cheese that blends well with cheddar.</p>
</div>

<div class="cheese-card">
<h2>Parmesan</h2>
<p>Strong flavor — perfect for topping baked mac and cheese.</p>
</div>

</section>

<section class="article-section">

<h2>Best Cheese Combinations</h2>

<ul>
<li>Cheddar + Gruyère</li>
<li>Cheddar + Gouda</li>
<li>Cheddar + Monterey Jack</li>
<li>Mozzarella + Parmesan</li>
</ul>

</section>

</main>

